{"tid":1207363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"13：30 物資站現需要以下物品：頭盔、清水、眼罩 (滑雪鏡約$20/ 個已可)、手套 (有軟膠面，非白色勞工手套)","createTime":"2019-06-12T06:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T07:04:35.000Z","uid":137493,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fd99555336b3691f091babc41c641b432c59e614","tid":1207363,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:09:06.000Z","msg":"13：30 物資站現需要以下物品， 希望前往之市民及同學可帶來：<br />\n頭盔、清水、眼罩 (滑雪鏡約$20/ 個已可)、手套 (有軟膠面，非白色勞工手套)、長及短遮、廚房用廁紙及紙巾。送往地點：中信大廈外及龍和道或其他物資站。請廣傳此訊息！"},{"pid":"6d2f46d9c9e1523efeaf323a714221109792f27c","tid":1207363,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:09:22.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"33c91a583bdf9820fccc8ba6a5df589866f06489","tid":1207363,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:09:35.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"91a27d8c3aa462a161be19181dedf6a81eaed259","tid":1207363,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:09:49.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"e6beb322194ba906bc7280a699518da4ba63a9d9","tid":1207363,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:10:02.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"56e6ff5a8b5f03a47955bab23ce158561a4de259","tid":1207363,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:10:16.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"020362344c06532c874609ff132799a610e9c435","tid":1207363,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:10:27.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"d5775e79c1e0ebb38fc8f86063f247a63688a818","tid":1207363,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:10:27.000Z","msg":"有人用棍拍野deam beat 既時候唔好劣<br />\n一齊叫同一句口號加士氣避免士氣此消彼長<br />\n有心理學背後原理<br />\n對陣口號可參考港隊打氣口號<br />\n拍拍~拍拍拍~DIE FOR HONG KONG<br />\n<br />\n引用 雞肉大師 巴打:<br />\n要佢哋一齊嘶哮， 進入同一個呼吸節奏 同一個心跳步伐 <br />\n配合戰鼓(你搵個大水樽好撚大嗰啲 求其搵嘢敲佢有節奏嘅)打拍子 就會將一堆散兵游勇聚合成一個群體<br />\n以往慣例邊個大聲公喇叭就死邊個， 二來呢啲設備貴<br />\n但係水樽就可以有好多個 水樽買得起<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外大家小心雙眼，戴眼罩被人噴油漆就喪失視力，唔戴又會比人插眼<br />\n<br />\n大家亦小心近距離突然由下巴向上大力推有機會導致頸椎受傷 請各位注意安全免生危險<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n希望無論大家去邊，甚至返工，不了<br />\n都想大家連日常生活都黑衫黑褲口罩笠帽加黑鞋<br />\n令到平時條街見到全黑既人唔再係特徵反而係大多數<br />\n最好個個用現金，咁買飛個個就唔係做突出個一個<br />\n<br />\n全民 BLACK BLOCK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203119</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJQsyEM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJQsyEM.png&h=fa55eabb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f41807f8c1457679bad85219df1b64cb3d1dedd","tid":1207363,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:10:41.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"ab952aa323148363322eecd97a6e35a4ec29287d","tid":1207363,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:10:55.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"30043dae71ac92d339127799cc842438e1e380d9","tid":1207363,"uid":1953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd99555336b3691f091babc41c641b432c59e614","tid":1207363,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:09:06.000Z","msg":"13：30 物資站現需要以下物品， 希望前往之市民及同學可帶來：<br />\n頭盔、清水、眼罩 (滑雪鏡約$20/ 個已可)、手套 (有軟膠面，非白色勞工手套)、長及短遮、廚房用廁紙及紙巾。送往地點：中信大廈外及龍和道或其他物資站。請廣傳此訊息！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:10:57.000Z","msg":"眼罩 手套邊度有得買"},{"pid":"14e7237ec7528a6c99e8e0070eeee1af8f1a506c","tid":1207363,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:11:07.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"e81e2f46ecc519b3bba9681c6d429c8f807e6594","tid":1207363,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:11:20.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"03d37b50ecfb61c8514b3259fde0c665ff25e003","tid":1207363,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"178cbcfd2b614c79e3590ebeb6dc3503e50dcf80","tid":1207363,"uid"